  "elapsed_s": 4.1,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So we found it out from them that there was an uprising.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And since the uprising, they didn't-- I think they brought in another transport after the uprising.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "If I'm not mistaken, there was another transport bringing in-- oh, but they had-- didn't have the-- the-- the-- the facilities already to gas them, so the-- they-- they-- they shot them.",
      "word_count": 32
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And-- and-- you know?",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And the-- the machine was working very-- you heard it, when you were [INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Until today, I cannot take that smell from-- from a steak.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I cannot even tell-- I hate-- I don't like a steak, because the burning from that meat, from the people, are the sell-- same smell than from the steak.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "So when I came back here to the United States, when they gave me a steak, I didn't want to eat the steak.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "I had that feeling, you see?",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "So you heard, constantly, [MACHINE SOUND] the machine was working.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "[MACHINE SOUND] The motor?",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "[INAUDIBLE] and taking out and [INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "It's thousands, and thousands, and thousands of people were there, murdered.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I found it out before I came to that camp.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Before I went to Treblinka, I found out from the Warsaw Ghetto.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Oh, [STAMMERING] Yeah, I didn't know that-- that-- then, I didn't believe it.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "It's not a question about I didn't know it-- know it, because people came back-- you know, they came back from there, from that place where they-- they assaulted them, shot them, and burned them, and put them in-- in the graves, in the-- not what-- people was in machines, you see?",
      "word_count": 52
    }
  ],
